<h4><%= content_tag(:a, "Can my kids bring toy weapons to CUCO?", name: "weapons") %></h4>
<p>Out of respect for families that choose not to play with toy guns, we ask that you not bring them to CUCO. Sometimes a nerf class is offered, and nerf guns are, of course, needed for that. They should only be played with in the class. During other times, if they are large or proving hard for kids to avoid, they can be stored out of sight behind a door by the stage.</p>

<p>Swords are fine to bring. "Boffer" weapons (large swords made of PVC and pool noodles) can be brought, but should not be played with in the auditorium or lobby. When the weather is nice, they should be used only outside. In bad weather, they can be used in the gym when it is available.</p>

